{"tid":2073133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本解除告急後觀光地人頭湧湧","createTime":"2020-06-21T05:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T11:59:58.000Z","uid":28114,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc6283bc6fc792e33398b1634f340932347ed3c","tid":2073133,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"【日本市況】解除告急後栃木縣內觀光地人頭湧湧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ntax6T3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtax6T3.jpg&h=13d625f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本各都道府縣解急後，栃木縣近日出現觀光地人潮，世遺日光東照宮、鬼怒川溫泉鄉、那須高原，以至宇都宮縣餃子勝地「宇都宮餃子會直營店」：来らっせ本店停候人龍也要 90分鐘，呈現短時間「報復式消費」。<br />\n新聞來源 下野新聞<br />\n移動自粛解除、栃木県内観光地にも人出<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shimotsuke.co.jp/articles/-/325447?top\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shimotsuke.co.jp%2Farticles%2F-%2F325447%3Ftop&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=04f12247\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shimotsuke.co.jp/articles/-/325447?top</a><br />\n==========================="},{"pid":"7b4aaa34d5602f0db7d01704741d7d983e4d30c3","tid":2073133,"uid":108201,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"宇都宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1118f420fc8e09b3b69a0471a7fabca80ca9dd2a","tid":2073133,"uid":134683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7b4aaa34d5602f0db7d01704741d7d983e4d30c3","tid":2073133,"uid":108201,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"宇都宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"觀光宇都宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5b97c6fcf93c061df35a6404bde72c7f4ead16","tid":2073133,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:57:24.000Z","msg":"宇都宮<br />\n好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class